  "title_full": "AN ACT INSTITUTIONALIZING THE TEACHING OF MEDIA LITERACY AS PART OF THE CURRICULUM OF BASIC AND SECONDARY EDUCATION, AND APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR",
  "title_short": "Media Literacy For The Youth Act Of 2025",
  "abstract": "Proposes several provisions regarding media platforms; digital communication skills; facts and opinions, misinformation/disinformation identification; fact-checking methods and information sources evaluation; online advertisements/different digital communities analysis; responsible and ethical use of the internet/social media; online safety, privacy, and cyber-hygiene; cyberbullying and online exploitation prevention; intellectual property and respect for digital content; constructive use of media for civic participation/learning/advocacy; mobile apps/tools navigation; Artificial Intelligence tech use; digital content an/information production.",
